{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"UIEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/sourceCapabilities\"><code>sourceCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/view\"><code>view</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/which\"><code>which</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<code>UIEvent</code>&nbsp;接口表示简单的用户界面事件。</p>\n\n<p><code>UIEvent</code>&nbsp;是从&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> 派生出来的。尽管 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>UIEvent.initUIEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 方法为了向后兼容而一直保留着，但是你应该使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\" title=\"UIEvent()\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a> 构造器来创建&nbsp;<code>UIEvent</code>&nbsp;对象。</p>\n\n<p>某些接口是这个的直接或间接后代：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TouchEvent\"><code>TouchEvent</code></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FocusEvent\"><code>FocusEvent</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/KeyboardEvent\"><code>KeyboardEvent</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/InputEvent\"><code>InputEvent</code></a>, 和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CompositionEvent\"><code>CompositionEvent</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructors","title":"Constructors","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"uievent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\" title=\"UIEvent()\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>创建一个&nbsp;<code>UIEvent</code>&nbsp;对象</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>也继承了父代&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> 的一些属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"uievent.cancelbubble_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelBubble\"><code>UIEvent.cancelBubble</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;<svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>，表示该事件的冒泡是否被取消。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"uievent.detail\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail\"><code>UIEvent.detail</code></a><span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a&nbsp;<code>long</code>&nbsp;with details about the event, depending on the event type.</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.ischar\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/isChar\"><code>UIEvent.isChar</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>，表示该事件是否产生了一个键盘字符（key character）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.layerx_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/layerX\"><code>UIEvent.layerX</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回事件相对于当前层的水平坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.layery_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/layerY\"><code>UIEvent.layerY</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回事件相对于当前层的垂直坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.pagex\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageX\"><code>UIEvent.pageX</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回事件相对于整个文档的水平坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.pagey\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/MouseEvent/pageY\"><code>UIEvent.pageY</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回事件相对于整个文档的垂直坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.sourcecapabilities_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/sourceCapabilities\"><code>UIEvent.sourceCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;<span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回输入设备功能接口的一个实例，它提供有关负责生成 touch 事件的物理设备的信息。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.view\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/view\"><code>UIEvent.view</code></a><span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回一个包含了产生该事件的视图的&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>WindowProxy</code></a> 。</dd>\n <dt id=\"uievent.which\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/which\"><code>UIEvent.which</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>返回一个对应（键盘）按下的数字类型的&nbsp;<code>keyCode</code>&nbsp;，或者一个字母数字键按下时的字符码 (<code>charCode</code>)。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>也继承了父代&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> 的一些方法。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"uievent.inituievent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>UIEvent.initUIEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>初始化一个&nbsp;<code>UIEvent</code>&nbsp;对象。如果事件已经被分派，这个方法什么都不做。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#idl-uievent","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.UIEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.UIEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/JavaScript/Building_blocks/Events\">Introduction to events</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructors","id":"constructors"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"UIEvent 接口表示简单的用户界面事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"UIEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"UIEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"UIEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"UIEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"UIEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/uievent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/uievent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent","title":"UIEvent"}],"pageTitle":"UIEvent - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}